<h3>Cannot enable Raspi 3 integrated bluetooth</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>I cannot for the life of me get the raspi 3 Bluetooth to work. Bluetooth status shows that it is &quot;inactive (dead).<br/>I have installed bluez and Bluetooth and yes I&#039;ve started Bluetooth but nothing will work for me. Please help.</p>
