<h3>Re: Cannot enable Raspi 3 integrated bluetooth</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>Try</p><div class="quotebox"><blockquote><div><p>sudo apt-get install pi-bluetooth</p></div></blockquote></div><p>To see the status:</p><div class="quotebox"><blockquote><div><p>systemctl status bluetooth</p></div></blockquote></div><p>To start bluetooth:</p><div class="quotebox"><blockquote><div><p>systemctl start bluetooth</p></div></blockquote></div><p>I cannot get pi-Bluetooth. I&#039;ve tried many times and it just says &quot;unable to locate package&quot;</p>
